  Locus:
    Page: 331
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Nature
---
Nature is a light, and by looking at Nature in her own light we will
understand her. Visible Nature can be seen in her visible light; invisible
Nature will become visible if we acquire the power to perceive her in her
inner light.
